column4: Lots missing here. You need to do some very simple research online to understand what these terms are.
Look up g-code. Look up .stl. Bed leveling is important if you want your print to
adhere properly to the print bed. Look up all the terms in this list and read about them.
Reference them and you can still get points without the pictures.
